{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/UIComponentsReference","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","metadata":{"title":"UI Components Reference","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"abstract":[{"text":"API reference for the ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" view modifiers — the SwiftUI surface of ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/uicomponentsreference"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The UI product layers three view modifiers on top of ","type":"text"},{"code":"RevenueCatUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Two primitives present the paywall and customer center directly from a ","type":"text"},{"code":"Binding<Bool>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; one convenience modifier composes both, driven by ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallState","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Each presentation modifier attaches to the modified content view directly — there are no ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" wrappers and no ","type":"text"},{"code":".background { … }","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" indirection. This shape is what makes the macOS sheet machinery present reliably.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For step-by-step wiring, see "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"How to Present the UI","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" in the "},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" documentation. For the rationale behind platform-specific behavior, see "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Platform Behavior","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" in the same catalog."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Library-target","level":2,"text":"Library target"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Product: ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Package.swift"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":[".product(name: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI\", package: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\"),"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The UI product depends on "},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"RevenueCatUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", both pulled in transitively. Apps that don’t ship paywall UI in the same target (for example, a tests-only target) can depend on the lower-level "},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" product alone."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Modifiers","level":2,"text":"Modifiers"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"revenueCatPaywallisPresentedofferingIdentifierdisplayCloseButtononDismiss","level":3,"text":"`revenueCatPaywall(isPresented:offeringIdentifier:displayCloseButton:onDismiss:)`"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["extension View {","    public func revenueCatPaywall(","        isPresented: Binding<Bool>,","        offeringIdentifier: String? = nil,","        displayCloseButton: Bool = true,","        onDismiss: (() -> Void)? = nil","    ) -> some View","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Attaches "},{"code":"RevenueCatUI.PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" as a platform-appropriate sheet."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"iOS","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" — Presents in a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fullScreenCover"},{"type":"text","text":" so the paywall takes the full screen."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"macOS"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Presents in a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sheet"},{"type":"text","text":" sized to a 400×600 minimum."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pass a real two-way binding; SwiftUI sets it to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":" on user dismissal. Build it from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState.isPresented"},{"type":"text","text":" so the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"set:"},{"type":"text","text":" closure dispatches "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".paywall(.dismiss)"},{"type":"text","text":" and the plugin clears its presentation state."}]},{"text":"Parameters","type":"heading","anchor":"Parameters","level":4},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"isPresented","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" — Two-way binding to the paywall’s visibility flag."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"offeringIdentifier","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" — Identifier of the RevenueCat offering to present, for a win-back or regional offer. Defaults to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", which presents the dashboard’s current offering. An unknown identifier or a failed fetch falls back to the current offering with a logged warning.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"displayCloseButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — Whether ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"text":" shows a close button. Defaults to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":". Neither the iOS ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fullScreenCover"},{"text":" nor the macOS ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sheet"},{"text":" offers any other dismissal affordance, so pass ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"text":" only for a hard paywall the user must purchase through.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onDismiss"},{"text":" — Optional callback fired after dismissal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"`revenueCatCustomerCenter(isPresented:onDismiss:)`","anchor":"revenueCatCustomerCenterisPresentedonDismiss","type":"heading","level":3},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["extension View {","    public func revenueCatCustomerCenter(","        isPresented: Binding<Bool>,","        onDismiss: (() -> Void)? = nil","    ) -> some View","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Attaches the customer center as a platform-appropriate sheet."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"iOS","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" — Presents "},{"code":"RevenueCatUI.CustomerCenterView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in a "},{"code":"sheet","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"macOS","type":"text"}]},{"text":" — Opens ","type":"text"},{"code":"itms-apps:\/\/apps.apple.com\/account\/subscriptions","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" via "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSWorkspace.shared.open"},{"type":"text","text":" (falling back to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"https:\/\/apps.apple.com\/account\/subscriptions"},{"type":"text","text":" web URL if nothing on the system handles the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"itms-apps"},{"type":"text","text":" scheme), immediately clears the binding, and fires "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onDismiss"},{"type":"text","text":". RevenueCatUI does not ship a customer center on macOS."}]}]}]},{"text":"Parameters","anchor":"Parameters","level":4,"type":"heading"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"isPresented","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — Two-way binding to the customer center’s visibility flag.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onDismiss"},{"text":" — Optional callback fired after dismissal (or, on macOS, after the App Store URL is opened).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"`revenueCatPaywall(state:offeringIdentifier:displayCloseButton:send:)`","anchor":"revenueCatPaywallstateofferingIdentifierdisplayCloseButtonsend","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["extension View {","    public func revenueCatPaywall(","        state: PaywallState,","        offeringIdentifier: String? = nil,","        displayCloseButton: Bool = true,","        send: @escaping (PaywallAction) -> Void","    ) -> some View","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Convenience modifier that attaches both ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatPaywall(isPresented:offeringIdentifier:displayCloseButton:onDismiss:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter(isPresented:onDismiss:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and dispatches the matching dismiss action when each sheet closes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The two presentations are mutually exclusive; the paywall wins. While "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state.isPresented"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" the customer-center binding reads "},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and a request for either surface while the other is up dispatches ","type":"text"},{"code":".dismissCustomerCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — the platform refuses simultaneous presentations, and this rule keeps ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState"},{"text":" from holding a flag the platform ignored. See ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Platform Behavior","type":"text"}]},{"text":" in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},{"text":" documentation.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"anchor":"Parameters","text":"Parameters","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" — The paywall slice from your store, typically "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"store.paywall"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"offeringIdentifier"},{"type":"text","text":" — Identifier of the RevenueCat offering to present. Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" (the dashboard’s current offering); see the primitive modifier above."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"displayCloseButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — Whether ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" shows a close button. Defaults to ","type":"text"},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; see the primitive modifier above.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"send","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — A closure that lifts a ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallAction","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" into your root action and dispatches it through the store. Typically ","type":"text"},{"code":"{ store.send(.paywall($0)) }","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Equivalent-manual-wiring","text":"Equivalent manual wiring","level":4,"type":"heading"},{"code":["ContentView()","    .revenueCatPaywall(","        isPresented: Binding(","            get: { store.paywall.isPresented },","            set: { if !$0 { store.send(.paywall(.dismiss)) } }","        )","    )","    .revenueCatCustomerCenter(","        isPresented: Binding(","            get: { store.paywall.isCustomerCenterPresented },","            set: { if !$0 { store.send(.paywall(.dismissCustomerCenter)) } }","        )","    )"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the convenience modifier when both sheets are needed; use the primitives when only one is needed or when you want to interleave other modifiers between them."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior"],"title":"Related Documentation","anchor":"Related-Documentation"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference"],"generated":true,"title":"Reference","anchor":"Reference"}],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall","title":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","abstract":[{"text":"RevenueCat adapter for Swidux’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallPlugin"},{"type":"text","text":". Implements "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" against "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchas